---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 text-gray-800">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-4">
      This page informs you about how the site <strong
        >jlg-consulting.com</strong
      > processes personal data, in accordance with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR).
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">No Automatic Collection</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
      The site does not automatically collect any personal data. No
      forms are present, and no tracking or analysis cookies are
      used.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">Contact by Email</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
      If you contact me voluntarily by email at <a
        href="mailto:jlg@jlg-consulting.com"
        class="text-green-700 underline">jlg@jlg-consulting.com</a
      >, the data you provide (name, email address, message content) will be used solely to respond to your request. This data will not be stored in a database or shared with third parties.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">Retention Period</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
      Email exchanges are kept only for as long as necessary to process your request, unless otherwise required by law.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">Your Rights</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
      In accordance with the GDPR, you have the right to access, rectify,
      delete, and limit the processing of your data. For any requests, you can write to: <a
        href="mailto:jlg@jlg-consulting.com"
        class="text-green-700 underline">jlg@jlg-consulting.com</a
      >.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">Data Controller</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
      Jean-Louis Guénégo
      <br />
      Contact: <a
        href="mailto:jlg@jlg-consulting.com"
        class="text-green-700 underline">jlg@jlg-consulting.com</a
      >
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>